### Create lead
POST http://localhost:8000/api/leads/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "+1 234 567 890",
  "pain_area": "Stress Relief",
  "pain_severity": "Moderate",
  "pain_duration": "3 Months",
  "treatments": ["Yoga", "Meditation"],
  "country": "Thailand",
  "travel_date": "2026-04-20",
  "urgency": "Flexible",
  "stay_length": "1 Week",
  "budget": "$2,000 - $4,000"
}

### Get auth token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### List leads
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leads/?status=new&ordering=-created_at
Authorization: Token your-token

### Get lead detail
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leads/{{lead_id}}/
Authorization: Token your-token

### Patch lead
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/leads/{{lead_id}}/
Authorization: Token your-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "contacted",
  "notes": "Reached out on WhatsApp."
}
